00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:06.160
Pahami itu, Piyush.

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:07.640
Ayo.

00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:28.560
Suvarna.

00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:46.440
Rukmini, ayo, tetangga
baru kita sudah datang.

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:47.680
Izinkan saya memperkenalkan Anda kepada mereka.

00:11:47.800 --> 00:11:48.880
Mereka datang enam bulan lalu.

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:58.840
Rupal, apa kabarmu?
Berikan beberapa berita.

00:11:58.960 --> 00:12:00.480
Kisah cinta baru di
jalan Hanuman kami.

00:12:00.600 --> 00:12:01.480
Kisah cinta?

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:03.000
Saya akan memberi Anda beritanya.
- Lanjutkan.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:05.440
Ibu Jhamkudi, tetangga kami.
- Ya.

00:12:05.560 --> 00:12:06.720
Apakah Anda ingat putranya Urmil?

00:12:06.840 --> 00:12:09.000
Reporternya?  - Benar.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:11.720
Saat ini, reporter itu
sendiri yang menjadi berita.

00:12:11.840 --> 00:12:14.640
Dia berselingkuh.
